@ENDNODE

############################################################################

@NODE BOGUE "Bugs"

  I am proud to tell you that MUIBank is 100% @{b}bug-free@{ub}!
I can assure you that thorough tests have been made to find them. To tell
you the truth, I also use MUIBank. However, if inspite of my diligence
you should encounter one of these satanic bugs, please report to @{" author " LINK AUTEUR}
by indicating your hardware and software configuration as well as which
version of MUIBank you are using.

@{b}Remember:@{ub} @{i}A bug known is a bug gone!@{ui}
            (No matter how vicious it might be!)

@ENDNODE

############################################################################

@NODE HIST "History"

  The history of MUIBank would like to point out the programm evolution.
The erdication of the bugs is not mentioned since this is an on-going
process.

@{b}1.62@{ub} (28/10/97)
    _ Addiction of the english documentation.

@{b}1.61@{ub} (18/09/97)
    _ Addiction of the english catalog.

@{b}1.60@{ub} (12/06/97)
    _ Addiction of the queries management. Transactions are now selected
      according to your criteria.
    _ Addiction of a button which allows to delete the filter.
    _ In the main window, the fields are now separated by a vertical bar.

@{b}1.52@{ub} (05/05/97):
    _ Eradication of an error in the storage files of the MUIBanque
      version 1.10. It is possible that the order of the display panels
      has changed. If this is the case, use the display window to restore
      the order.

@{b}1.51@{ub} (15/04/97):
    _ The file MUIBank can be renamed without ignoring the tooltypes.
    _ When the filter is used, a total of the anterior and posterior
      operations can be displayed in the filter..
    _ The date set-up is no longer limited; you can type 3.5.1997
      instead of 03.05.1997.
    _ The date separator can be changed.
    _ Multiple date formats are available.
    _ The comma position in the amount can be changed.

@{b}1.50@{ub} (07/04/97):
    _ Addition of an automatic operation administration as well as an
      associated property dialog box.

@{b}1.40@{ub} (17/03/97):
    _ MUIBank makes specific versions available now for different processors.
    _ Addition of the print option as well as a print property dialog box.

@{b}1.30@{ub} (06/01/97):
    _ Addition of a filter which allows you to select the operations following
      their transmission dates.
    _ Addition of an option which allows you to reverse the meaning of the
      "*"-dialog box.

@{b}1.20@{ub} (14/12/96):
    _ Application localisation. MUIBanque changed it's name to MUIBank.
      The ToolType COMPTE has been renamed to ToolType ACCOUNT.
    _ Modification of the Display window.

@{b}1.11@{ub} (24/11/96):
    _ Addition of the ToolType COMPTE which allows you to open an account
      during the instalation of MUIBanque.

@{b}1.10@{ub} (03/11/96):
    _ All characters are accepted in the Number dialog box of an operation.
    _ Addition of the Operation, the dialog box and renaming of the Date
      dialog box into Transmission dialog box to distinguish the transmission
      date from the date that it actually took place.
    _ Addition of the "*" dialog box to distinguish the operations which are
      configured after the reopening of the account.
    _ Implementation of different types of balance.
    _ Implementation of a choice of panels to be displayed in the main list.

@{b}1.00@{ub} (13/10/96):
    _ First public version of MUIBanque.

@ENDNODE

